Package: com.yourname.homepodaudiobridge
Name: HomePod Audio Bridge
Version: 0.0.1
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Streams beam-formed mic audio to Home Assistant via Wyoming protocol over TCP.
             Hooks mediaserverd's AudioUnitRender to capture echo-cancelled PCM and forward
             it to a central Wyoming/openWakeWord intake. Preserves AirPlay natively.
Maintainer: Joe Black <joe@joeblack.nyc>
Author: Joe Black <joe@joeblack.nyc>
Section: Tweaks
